%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20CEO%20who%20microdoses%20magic%20mushrooms%20to%20feel%20like%20my%20best%20self%20at%20work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20in%20a%20white%20shirt%20holding%20Gyan%20mudra%20(hand%20posture%20formed%20by%20joining%20the%20tips%20of%20the%20index%20finger%20and%20thumb)%20with%20a%20glowing%20mushroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6644a650b4abc992e8c9a077%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKiana%C2%A0Anvaripour%2C%C2%A0%20a%2042-year-old%20CEO%20living%20in%20L.A.%20has%20always%20been%20dedicated%20to%20feeling%20her%20best.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20Anvaripour%20began%20experiencing%20perimenopause%2C%20she%20looked%20to%20enhance%20her%20wellness%20routine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20executive%20began%20microdosing%20%26quot%3Bmagic%20mushrooms%26quot%3B%20alongside%20eating%20well%2C%20taking%20vitamins%20and%20daily%20workouts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Kiana%20Anvaripour%20a%2042-year-old%20CEO%20and%20mother%20of%20two%20living%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity%20and%20reflects%20only%20the%20views%20of%20Ms.%20Anvaripour%2C%20who%20is%20not%20a%20medical%20professional.%20Psilocybin%20is%20still%20illegal%20in%20the%20US%20federally%20and%20in%20most%20states.%20There%20is%20no%20medical%20consensus%20about%20its%20potential%20benefits%2C%20including%20those%20described%20below%2C%20and%20the%20drugs%20come%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fare-magic-mushrooms-dangerous-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Erisks%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20remember%2C%20I've%20been%20on%20a%20quest%20to%20feel%20my%20very%20best.%20As%20I've%20gotten%20older%2C%20wellness%20has%20become%20even%20more%20important%20to%20me%2C%20especially%20in%20combating%20the%20symptoms%20of%20my%20menstrual%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20mom%20of%20two%20daughters%20under%2010%20and%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20creative%20agency%20in%20LA%2C%20I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20better%20parent%20and%20leader.%20Sleep%2C%20exercise%2C%20meditation%2C%20and%20plant-based%20supplements%20have%20all%20helped%20me%20achieve%20those%20goals%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20approaching%20perimenopause%20a%20little%20over%20two%20years%20ago.%20Even%20with%20my%20wellness%20routine%2C%20I%20had%20this%20sense%20of%20overwhelm%20as%20I%20tried%20to%20juggle%20so%20many%20responsibilities.%20I%20was%20open%20to%20trying%20a%20natural%20tool%20to%20help%20me%20navigate%20this%20new%20and%20frustrating%20phase%20in%20my%20life.%20I%20was%20experiencing%20all%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fperimenopause-symptoms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esymptoms%20of%20perimenopause%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20often%20hear%20about%3A%20brain%20fog%2C%20mood%20swings%2C%20and%20challenges%20sleeping.%20The%20list%20goes%20on%20and%20on.%20I%20wanted%20more%20support%20and%20heard%20about%20the%20wonders%20of%20micro-dosing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20the%20wellness%20industry%2C%20I%20had%20previously%20researched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-microdosing-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicrodosing%20with%20psilocybin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20knew%20of%20friends%2C%20colleagues%2C%20and%20other%20CEOs%20who%20used%20it%20for%20productivity%20in%20the%20workplace.%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20California%2C%20psilocybin%2C%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20wellness%20plant%20medicine%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrodosing-psilocybin-mushrooms-for-creativity-startups-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommon%20and%20not%20hard%20to%C2%A0come%20by%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20people%20use%20it%20for%20performance%20and%20health%20and%20some%20who%20have%20adopted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fwellness%2F2024%2Fapr%2F11%2Fcalifornia-sober-meaning-marijuana%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECali-sober%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20use%20it%20as%20a%20replacement%20for%20alcohol%20to%20wind%20down.%20I'm%20not%20a%20doctor%20or%20medical%20expert%20and%20I%20can%20only%20speak%20to%20my%20own%20experience.%20My%20work%20in%20the%20wellness%20industry%20means%20I%20can%20try%20innovative%20brands%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthousands-sign-up-trip-first-legal-magic-mushroom-center-oregon-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant%20medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20trusted%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20approached%20past%20clients%20and%20friends%20about%20finding%20a%20product%20to%20try.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-hottest-startups-in-the-psychedelics-industry-vcs-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethings%20being%20sold%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20important%20to%20qualify%20the%20product%20I%20would%20use%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20micro%20or%20even%20nano%20dose%20I%20would%20take%2C%20specifically%20for%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20simply%20another%20addition%20to%20my%20whole-body%20wellness%20routine.%20Every%20day%2C%20I%20wake%20at%205%20a.m.%2C%20have%20lemon%20water%2C%20meditate%2C%20drink%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%2C%20work%20out%2C%20eat%20a%20high-protein%20breakfast%2C%20and%20then%20take%20my%20vitamins%20and%C2%A0a%20micro%20blend%20of%C2%A0psilocybin%C2%A0in%20capsule%20form.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20took%20a%20microdose%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20a%20difference.%20Even%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20later%2C%20I%20didn't%20notice%20a%20difference.%20But%20after%20a%20few%20weeks%20of%20consistently%20taking%20my%20microdose%2C%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20great.%26quot%3B%20Within%20weeks%2C%20I%20felt%20more%20focused%2C%20calm%2C%20and%20clear.%20I%20also%20felt%20more%20present%20and%20like%20the%20best%20version%20of%20myself.%20This%20change%20I%20attribute%20to%20microdosing%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20always%20been%20health%20conscious%2C%20but%20I%20began%20following%20a%20stricter%20daily%20routine%20after%20feeling%20the%20impact%20of%20perimenopause.%20Clean%20eating%2C%20eight%20hours%20of%20sleep%2C%20meditation%2C%20exercise%2C%20vitamins%2C%20plus%20psilocybin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20work%2C%20I%20have%20felt%20more%20focused%20since%20microdosing.%20I%20have%20communicated%20goals%20and%20needs%20clearly%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20where%20I%20am%20in%20my%20menstrual%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFemale%20CEOs%20can%20do%20everything%20male%20CEOs%20can%20do.%20But%20as%20women%20in%20business%2C%20we%20have%20to%20do%20it%20all%20on%20top%20of%20managing%20our%20periods%2C%20postpartum%20hormones%2C%20perimenopause%2C%20and%20menopause.%20We%20have%20physiological%20hurdles%20we%20have%20to%20overcome%20that%20men%20do%20not.%20I've%20found%20that%20microdosing%20helps%20me%20manage%20these.%20It%20is%20also%20prevalent%20in%20the%20biohacking%20and%20athlete%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20speaking%20openly%20about%20how%20microdosing%20has%20helped%20me%20cope%20with%20symptoms%20of%20perimenopause%2C%20so%20many%20other%20female%20leaders%20got%20in%20touch%20to%20say%20they%20felt%20seen.%20They%20had%20been%20looking%20for%20something%20to%20help%20them%20with%20the%20symptoms%20of%20aging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20hasn't%20just%20had%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20my%20ability%20to%20work%3B%20it's%20also%20improved%20how%20I%20interact%20with%20my%20employees.%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20can%20empathize%20more%20deeply%20with%20my%20employees%20and%20colleagues.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20an%20increase%20in%20people%20dealing%20with%20mental%20health%20problems.%20You%20want%20to%20listen%20and%20be%20there%20for%20your%20team%20as%20a%20leader.%20When%20I%20feel%20calm%20and%20focused%2C%20rather%20than%20overwhelmed%2C%20I%20can%20listen%20with%20more%20empathy%2C%20understand%2C%20and%20hold%20space%20with%20my%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20problems%20arise%2C%20as%20they%20always%20will%20in%20business%2C%20I%20start%20from%20a%20calm%20place%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20solution%2C%20communicating%20with%20my%20team%20empathetically%20to%20come%20to%20a%20solution.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20see%20it%20as%20a%20magic%20pill%20but%20as%20part%20of%20my%20wellness%20routine%20that%20helps%20optimize%20my%20mind%20and%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrodose-magic-mushrooms-increase-productivity-at-work-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715776108000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrodose-magic-mushrooms-increase-productivity-at-work-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20CEO%20who%20started%20mircodosing%20psilocybin%20or%20%26quot%3Bmagic%20mushrooms%26quot%3B%20shares%20how%20it%20helps%20her%20manage%20symptoms%20of%20perimenopause%20and%20be%20more%20productive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Crosby%20Medlicott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%20Co-Production%20%E2%80%98Papa%20Buka%E2%80%99%20Sets%20July%20Shoot%20