%20some%20tokens%2C%20Kaiko%20Research%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20event%20has%20left%20miners%20with%20fewer%20rewards%20while%20operating%20costs%20remain%20high.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThese%20firms%20haven't%20yet%20had%20to%20tap%20their%20bitcoin%20hoards%20thanks%20to%20high%20transaction%20fees%2C%20but%20that%20could%20change.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20have%20long%20considered%20bitcoin's%20recent%20halving%20as%20a%20major%20price%20bolster%2C%20but%20it%20could%20bring%20a%20wave%20of%20selling%20from%20one%20corner%20of%20the%20sector%2C%C2%A0according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fresearch.kaiko.com%2Finsights%2Freality-bites-for-btc-miners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKaiko%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20April%20halving%20is%20a%20pre-coded%20event%20in%20which%20the%20amount%20of%20bitcoin%20rewarded%20to%20crypto%20miners%20is%20slashed%20in%20half.%20Last%20month's%20halving%20was%20the%20fourth%20in%2012%20years%20and%20lowered%20daily%20token%20production%20from%20900%20to%20450%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-05-13%2Fbitcoin-miners-begin-to-feel-pressure-of-lower-token-rewards-kaiko-says%3Fsrnd%3Dmarkets-vp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20dramatic%20decrease%20in%20supply%20can%20push%20up%20the%20token's%20price%2C%20it%20also%20adds%20sizable%20costs%20to%20miner%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMining%20firms%20are%20only%20awarded%20bitcoin%20when%20they%20successfully%20complete%20a%20blockchain%20transaction%2C%20which%20is%20a%20resource-intensive%20process%20%E2%80%94%20with%20less%20bitcoin%20received%20to%20cover%20costs%2C%20halving%20tends%20to%20be%20a%20selling%20event%20for%20miners%2C%20Kaiko%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20this%20hasn't%20happened%2C%20as%20firms%20have%20instead%20depended%20on%20high%20transaction%20fees%20for%20funding%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20bitcoin%20given%20to%20miners%20for%20their%20service%20in%20confirming%20transactions.%20According%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20fees%20jumped%20amid%20a%20burst%20of%20meme-coin%20creation%20after%20the%20halving%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20example%2C%20transaction%20fees%20comprised%2016%25%20of%20bitcoin%20received%20by%20Marathon%20Digital%20in%20April%2C%20compared%20to%204.5%25%20in%20March%2C%20Kaiko%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20recent%20decline%20in%20fees%20could%20lead%20to%20selling%20pressure%20from%20miners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiners%20are%20often%20known%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-price-forecast-100000-crypto-spring-spot-etf-mining-halving-2023-11%5C%22%3Ehoarding%20bitcoin%20troves%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20selling%2C%20which%20analysts%20have%20previously%20pointed%20out%20as%20another%20price-boosting%20supply%20constraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20instance%2C%20Marathon%20Digital%20holds%2017%2C631%20BTC%20worth%20just%20over%20%241.1%20billion%2C%20while%20Riot%20Platforms%20hold%20another%208%2C872%20BTC%20worth%20over%20%24500%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaiko%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIf%20miners%20were%20forced%20to%20sell%20even%20a%20fraction%20of%20their%20holdings%20over%20the%20coming%20month%20this%20would%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kaiko%20did%20not%20outline%20how%20this%20could%20impact%20bitcoin's%20price%2C%20analyst%20Peter%20Brandt%20has%20separately%20argued%20that%20bitcoin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-prediction-crash-bull-rally-over-crypto-peter-brandt-2024-4%5C%22%3Ecould%20drop%20to%20the%20mid-%2430%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20post-halving%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid