resident's%20assent%20but%20the%20rules%20under%20which%20the%20Indian%20citizenship%20was%20granted%20were%20issued%20only%20on%20March%2011%20this%20year%20after%20over%20four%20years%20delay.%C2%A0The%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20which%20committed%20to%20enacting%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Bill%20in%20its%202019%20manifesto%2C%20said%20the%20implementation%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20drew%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20which%20terms%20the%20move%20as%20discriminatory%20and%20motivated%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20Centre%2C%20however%2C%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20CAA%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20prevent%20any%20persecuted%20Muslim%20for%20practising%20their%20version%20of%20Islam%2C%20from%20applying%20for%20Indian%20citizenship%20under%20the%20existing%20laws%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20witnessed%20protests%20against%20the%20decision%20to%20implement%20CAA%20as%20some%20fear%20the%20law%20could%20be%20used%20to%20declare%20them%20illegal%20immigrants%20and%20take%20away%20their%20Indian%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20denies%20this%20and%20says%20the%20law%20is%20needed%20to%20help%20minorities%20facing%20persecution%20in%20Muslim-majority%20nations%20as%20per%20the%20%26quot%3Bevergreen%20generous%20culture%20of%20India%20to%20get%20Indian%20citizenship%20for%20their%20happy%20and%20prosperous%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Indian%20citizen%20would%20be%20asked%20to%20produce%20any%20document%20to%20prove%20citizenship%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20headed%20by%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20said%2C%20adding%C2%A0the%20Citizenship%20Act%20doesn't%20deal%20with%20the%20deportation%20of%20illegal%20immigrants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715773920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F1ueom3g8_caa-certificate_625