com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-carthago-delenda-est-latin-t-shirt-explained-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715773233000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664496dc9686a6f37bfffc30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-carthago-delenda-est-latin-t-shirt-explained-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCarthago%20delenda%20est%26quot%3B%20means%20%26quot%3BCarthage%20must%20be%20destroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20popular%20idea%20from%20Rome%20in%20150%20BC.%20For%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20it%20has%20a%20personal%20significance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kcorcoran%40businessinsider.com%20(Kieran%20Corcoran)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-carthago-delenda-est-latin-t-shirt-explained-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Freak%20Accident%2C%20Scottish%20Aristocrat%20Dies%20After%20Falling%20From%20Bedroom%20Window%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2098-year-old%20aristocrat%20has%20died%20after%20falling%20out%20of%20his%20bedroom%20window%20while%20letting%20his%20cat%20out%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F05%2F15%2Faristocrat-98-falls-death-window-letting-cat-20840831%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAn%2520aristocrat%2520has%2520died%2520after%2Che%2520hit%2520a%2520concrete%2520patio.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20incident%20happened%20on%20May%2012%20when%C2%A0Michael%20Sydney%20Cedric%20Brudenell-Bruce%2C%20Marquess%20of%20Ailesbury%20fell%20out%20of%20his%20bedroom%20window%20and%20hit%20a%20concrete%20patio%20at%20his%20London%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20the%20incident%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20Teresa%20Marshall%20de%20Paoli%2C%2088%20said%2C%20''It%20was%20an%20absolutely%20freak%20accident.%20I%20think%20the%20cat%20called%20Honeybun%20got%20her%20head%20stuck%20and%20he%20pushed%20it%20(the%20window)%20up%20and%20lost%20his%20balance%20and%20fell%20onto%20the%20patio.%20He%20hit%20the%20concrete%20with%20the%20back%20of%20his%20head.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20been%C2%A0lying%20there%20for%20over%20an%20hour%20before%20she%20found%20him.%20She%20then%20immediately%C2%A0contacted%20police%20and%20her%20daughter%2C%20Lady%20Kathryn%20Brudenell%20Bruce%20who%20arrived%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Paoli%20further%20revealed%20that%C2%A0her%20husband%20had%20been%20suffering%20from%20dementia%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-t%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bn%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BblueLinks%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20lived%20together%20at%20their%20terraced%20home%20in%20Shepherd's%20Bush%2C%20west%20London%2C%20for%2014%20years%20after%20moving%20from%20Wiltshire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Met%20Police%20said%2C%20''Police%20were%20called%20by%20the%20London%20Ambulance%20Service%20at%208.05%20pm%20on%20Sunday%2C%20May%2012%2C%20to%20an%20address%20in%20Abdale%20Road%2C%20W12%2C%20after%20a%20man%20in%20his%2090s%20was%20found%20deceased.%20Officers%20and%20London%20Ambulance%20Service%20attended.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Paoli%2C%20who%20had%20been%20his%20partner%20for%2036%20years%20said%20the%20police%20treated%20the%20death%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrime%20scene%26quot%3B%20although%20she%20was%20not%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%2C%20''They%20thought%20I%20might%20have%20killed%20him%20before%20they%20realised%20he%20had%20fallen%20out%20of%20the%20window.%20It%20was%20an%20absolutely%20freak%20accident.%20There%20had%20not%20been%20a%20row%20%E2%80%93%20I%20had%20not%20hit%20him.%C2%A0He%20hit%20the%20concrete%20with%20back%20of%20head%20%E2%80%93%20I%20was%20told%20that%20would%20have%20killed%20him.%20He%20could%20have%20been%20lying%20there%20an%20hour%2C%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half.%20He%20was%20cold%20and%20very%20pale.%20I%20got%20a%20cush