%20men%20are%20better%20drivers%20than%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrawing%20on%20data%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onisr.securite-routiere.gouv.fr%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2022-09%2FObs_comportements_2021_v0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrance's%20National%20Interministerial%20Road%20Safety%20Observatory%202022-2023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20campaign%20noted%20that%2084%25%20of%20fatal%20accidents%20are%20caused%20by%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20according%20to%20a%20French%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onisr.securite-routiere.gouv.fr%2Fen%2Froad-safety-performance%2Fannual-road-safety-reports%2F2022-road-safety-annual-report%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPublication%2520on%25204th%2520October%252C%25202023%2C10.3%2525%2520higher%2520than%2520in%25202021.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%203%2C550%20people%20were%20killed%20on%20the%20roads%20in%20mainland%20France%20and%20its%20overseas%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20look%20at%20the%20figures%2C%20they%20are%20clear%3A%20to%20stay%20alive%20behind%20the%20wheel%2C%20the%20best%20thing%20for%20men%20to%20do%20is%20adopt%20the%20same%20behavior%20as%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20campaign's%20website%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVictimes%20%26amp%3B%20Citoyens%20also%20cited%20data%20showing%20that%2088%25%20of%20young%20drivers%20are%20killed%20by%20men%2C%2093%25%20of%20drunk%20drivers%20involved%20in%20accidents%20are%20men%2C%20and%20women%20are%20eight%20times%20less%20likely%20than%20their%20male%20counterparts%20to%20have%20a%20fatal%20accident%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStatistically%2C%20driving%20like%20a%20woman%20means%20only%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20staying%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20said%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20awareness%20campaign%20will%20run%20across%20print%2C%20digital%2C%20and%20metro%20platforms%2C%20and%20will%20also%20use%20a%20chatbot%20to%20respond%20to%20posts%20on%20X%20about%20women%20driving.%20according%20to%20the%20campaign's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iihs.org%2Ftopics%2Ffatality-statistics%2Fdetail%2Fmales-and-females%23trends%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsurance%20Institute%20for%20Highway%20Safety%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20number%20of%20male%20crash%20deaths%20was%20more%20than%20twice%20the%20number%20of%20female%20crash%20deaths%20for%20almost%20every%20year%20between%201975%20to%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%20said%20this%20could%20be%20attributed%20to%20men%20typically%20driving%20more%20miles%20than%20women%20but%20also%20being%20more%20likely%20to%20engage%20in%20risky%20driving%20practices%2C%20such%20as%20speeding%2C%20not%20wearing%20seatbelts%2C%20and%20driving%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20men%20have%20faced%20higher%20insurance%20premiums%2C%20as%20insurance%20companies%20see%20them%20as%20a%20greater%20risk%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhich-gender-pays-more-car-insurance-185411405.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Yahoo!%20Finance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrench-people-told-drive-like-women-reduce-traffic-accidents-deaths-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715768416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664482c7f27898f532d7bc15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrench-people-told-drive-like-women-reduce-traffic-accidents-deaths-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20French%20road%20safety%20group%20is%20telling%20people%20to%20%26quot%3Bdrive%20like%20a%20woman%26quot%3B%20to%20cut%20traffic%20deaths%2C%20pushing%20back%20on%20stereotypes%20that%20men%20are%20better%20drivers.%22%2C