E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20social%20angle%20is%20one%20of%20the%20contributing%20factors%2C%20our%20products%20have%20also%20become%20popular%20for%20their%20durability%20and%20better%20finish%20compared%20to%20other%20eco-friendly%20products%20like%20bamboo.%20While%20bamboo%20products%20are%20prone%20to%20fungal%20attack%2C%20there%20is%20no%20such%20worry%20in%20pine%20needle%20products%20as%20they%20are%20naturally-resistant%20to%20fungus%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20startup%2C%20Nupur%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20able%20to%20contribute%20towards%20society%20in%20a%20positive%20way.%20Interestingly%2C%20we%20have%20not%20observed%20any%20forest%20fires%20as%20of%20yet%20in%20the%20areas%20from%20where%20we%20collect%20pine%20needles.%20Earlier%2C%20at%20least%20three%20incidents%20were%20reported%20every%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20diverted%2020%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20to%20something%20useful.%20This%20is%20a%20small%20step%20towards%20a%20big%20issue%20but%20it%20can%20be%20replicated%20in%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20state%20to%20reduce%20the%20root%20cause%20and%20frequency%20of%20forest%20fires%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Sharvari%20Poharkar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Futtarakhand-wildfire-forest-fires-death-toll-rain-forecast-pushkar-singh-dhami-revenue-loss-2535698-2024-05-06%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5%20dead%20in%20Uttarakhand%20wildfires%2C%20over%201%2C000%20hectares%20of%20forest%20destroyed%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20Ankit%20Sharma%20for%20India%20Today%2C%20published%20on%206%20May%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5C