%20of%20180%20days%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20constitutional%20mandate%20for%20women%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20%E2%80%94%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20%E2%80%94%20emphasised%20that%20denying%20such%20leave%20forces%20women%20to%20resign.%20%E2%80%9CParticipation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20workforce%20is%20not%20a%20privilege%20but%20a%20constitutional%20mandate.%20Child%20care%20leave%20subserves%20an%20important%20constitutional%20objective%20to%20make%20women%20be%20part%20of%20the%20workforce.%20Otherwise%2C%20mothers%20will%20be%20left%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs%20to%20look%20after%20their%20children%20in%20critical%20phases%20of%20their%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20not%20concealed%20that%20Indian%20women%20have%20long%20been%20burdened%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98motherhood%20penalty%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatistically%20speaking%2C%2073%20percent%20of%20Indian%20women%20leave%20their%20jobs%20after%20giving%20birth%3B%2050%20percent%20leave%20their%20jobs%20to%20take%20care%20of%20their%20children%3B%20and%20even%20among%20those%20who%20manage%20to%20return%2C%2048%20percent%20drop%20out%20within%20four%20months%20of%20rejoining%20the%20workforce.%20Another%20survey%20reveals%20that%2030%20percent%20of%20women%20report%20getting%20wage%20cuts%20after%20maternity%20breaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChennai%E2%80%99s%20Sankari%20Sudhar%20went%20through%20the%20same%20agony%20after%20becoming%20a%20mother.%20After%20facing%20multiple%20rejections%2C%20she%20went%20on%20to%20start%20%E2%80%98Overqualified%20Housewives%E2%80%99%20to%20get%20women%20like%20her%20back%20into%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Foverqualified-housewives-3-1715314